31:49.252 --> 31:51.303
Thanks. Douchebag.

31:55.265 --> 31:56.641
Hey!

31:57.183 --> 31:58.893
Hi!

31:59.227 --> 32:02.480
So? How was the rest of your funeral?

32:02.515 --> 32:04.282
Oh, it was great.

32:04.317 --> 32:06.049
It totally bombed.

32:07.485 --> 32:09.877
So? Are we okay?

32:11.155 --> 32:15.868
Daniel. I am the worst coward there is.

32:15.903 --> 32:17.745
Yeah. Well. We all avoided you

32:17.829 --> 32:19.664
then, when we were playing quarters.

32:19.664 --> 32:21.791
No.

32:23.125 --> 32:24.935
I can't keep going.

32:26.629 --> 32:28.798
Okay, time out.

32:28.881 --> 32:30.733
Don't decide anything just yet. Okay?

32:30.733 --> 32:33.591
Because I got something.

32:34.971 --> 32:37.076
Look, I'm going to Switzerland.

32:37.515 --> 32:39.970
They got this experimental treatment in

32:40.005 --> 32:42.425
St Moritz that I… scammed my way into.

32:43.813 --> 32:45.850
And I don't know if it's gonna work.

32:45.850 --> 32:48.726
But I figure it's worth a shot.

32:49.693 --> 32:53.615
And if it does, I'll be back.

32:54.316 --> 32:57.201
And then decide. Okay?

32:58.244 --> 32:59.641
Okay.

33:14.218 --> 33:16.806
You're going off like a dog aren't you?

33:19.264 --> 33:20.480
What do you mean?

33:20.724 --> 33:23.525
When a dog knows it's gonna die

33:23.560 --> 33:27.564
he goes off into the woods by itself and uh,

33:27.599 --> 33:30.673
rich guys go to St Moritz.

33:32.611 --> 33:35.376
They have beautiful woods there.

33:38.450 --> 33:40.625
Yes, they do.

33:42.788 --> 33:44.934
I'll see you, Guido.

33:46.124 --> 33:48.232
See ya.

34:00.222 --> 34:02.182
Ms Levine took her shirt off.

34:02.217 --> 34:04.316
That is not in dispute.

34:04.351 --> 34:06.916
And she did it to make
a political point.

34:06.951 --> 34:09.516
Now people make political points every day.

34:09.516 --> 34:11.560
The TV, the press, on the internet,

34:11.560 --> 34:13.985
expressing opinions of all kinds

34:14.069 --> 34:16.487
without breaking the law.

34:16.523 --> 34:18.150
For Ms Levine, our country's

34:18.150 --> 34:21.291
guarantee of free speech wasn't enough.

34:21.326 --> 34:24.364
Our guarantee of freedom of assembly?
Wasn't enough.

34:24.364 --> 34:26.643
And apparently our guarantee of

34:26.679 --> 34:28.924
freedom of the press wasn't enough.

34:28.958 --> 34:31.538
None of these freedoms
were enough for Ms Levine

34:31.538 --> 34:33.880
and the point she had to make. No.

34:33.915 --> 34:36.027
She had to break the law by

34:36.062 --> 34:39.391
violating our community standards of decency.

34:39.427 --> 34:42.722
No one violated Ms Levine's freedom of speech!

34:42.757 --> 34:47.851
Ms Levine violated our community laws.

34:48.186 --> 34:50.897
Don't let her get away with it.

34:56.360 --> 34:57.987
Jake Watson convicted of

34:58.071 --> 34:59.920
molesting an eight-year-old girl.

34:59.920 --> 35:01.741
Served two years, then convicted of

35:01.741 --> 35:03.701
molesting an eleven-year-old girl.

35:03.701 --> 35:07.205
John Bauers, convicted of multiple counts of rape.

35:07.246 --> 35:10.875
Calvin Stevens, convicted of sodomizing and

35:10.910 --> 35:14.504
molesting over a dozen boys ages six to ten.

35:15.254 --> 35:17.792
This is a list of registered sex-offenders.

35:17.792 --> 35:19.652
This is the list the prosecutor

35:19.675 --> 35:21.469
thinks Ms Levine should be put on.

35:21.469 --> 35:26.015
This is the company they think she belongs in.

35:26.265 --> 35:27.607
Do you?

35:27.642 --> 35:30.402
Do any of you think that a woman who

35:30.437 --> 35:33.163
bared her breasts at a political rally

35:33.792 --> 35:35.352
poses the same risk to the

35:35.366 --> 35:38.903
community as rapists and child molesters?

35:39.035 --> 35:42.695
Of course you don't.  And I'll let you
in on a little secret.

35:44.033 --> 35:45.333
Neither do they.

35:45.368 --> 35:48.496
You see they arrested Ms Levine and the
other women

35:48.531 --> 35:51.651
before and charged them
with ‘disturbing the peace’.

35:51.707 --> 35:54.585
When a woman is arrested for

35:54.668 --> 35:57.505
sunbathing topless in a public park,

35:57.588 --> 35:59.676
she's either charged with disturbing

35:59.676 --> 36:01.694
the peace or more likely the cop says,

36:01.694 --> 36:06.554
“Hey, lady put your shirt back on”. And
then he goes off to deal with real crime.

36:06.805 --> 36:08.898
So why is Ms Levine different?

36:08.933 --> 36:12.519
Because she was protesting redistricting.

36:12.554 --> 36:13.832
Now, I know that may sound

36:13.832 --> 36:17.031
arcane and theoretical to you.

36:17.066 --> 36:20.194
But I assure you that to the politicians in power,

36:20.229 --> 36:22.988
there is nothing more dear to their hearts.

36:23.023 --> 36:24.780
If Ms Levine had written a scholarly

36:24.780 --> 36:27.987
article about redistricting
for an obscure journal

36:28.022 --> 36:30.319
that nobody would ever have read, the

36:30.354 --> 36:32.062
District Attorney wouldn't have cared at all.

36:32.062 --> 36:35.053
But she and the other women

36:35.088 --> 36:38.045
made their argument topless.

36:38.128 --> 36:39.921
People paid attention
because, let's face it,

36:39.921 --> 36:41.609
when two hundred women take their

36:41.609 --> 36:43.227
tops off, people are going to look.

36:43.227 --> 36:46.195
But after they've gawked for a minute
they might ask,

36:46.195 --> 36:48.415
“Why have they taken their tops off”?

36:48.847 --> 36:52.404
And then they might find out
it's because of redistricting.

36:52.893 --> 36:55.958
And then they might say, “Well, what is that?”

36:55.993 --> 36:58.573
And then when they find out they might say,

36:59.121 --> 37:04.442
“Oh my God!  Our politicians have
highjacked our Democracy”.

37:05.040 --> 37:07.211
The prosecutor charged Ms Levine

37:07.246 --> 37:12.746
for violating our community standards.

37:13.133 --> 37:15.255
This is Boston.

37:15.290 --> 37:17.924
Home of the Tea Party.

37:17.959 --> 37:20.622
Home of the people and the spirit of

37:20.657 --> 37:24.341
freedom that literally created this country.

37:24.376 --> 37:26.648
Our community standard is that we

37:26.683 --> 37:29.081
won't be silenced by the King of England,

37:29.081 --> 37:30.799
much less the District Attorney!

37:30.799 --> 37:34.979
Our community standard is that we speak
the truth to power.

37:35.101 --> 37:39.272
And if those in power don't like it…

37:39.564 --> 37:41.816
…too bad.

38:00.668 --> 38:03.441
Oh, look at you. This is terrible.

38:04.526 --> 38:06.154
I'll tell you what I'll do, Garry.

38:06.154 --> 38:06.608
Garrett.

38:06.608 --> 38:08.978
I'm not in the office all the time.

38:09.013 --> 38:11.296
I mean I'm very busy over lunch and

38:11.331 --> 38:13.635
morning break and afternoon coffee.

38:13.670 --> 38:15.907
That would leave three or four hours

38:15.942 --> 38:18.144
when I won't need the office at all.

38:18.179 --> 38:20.451
Make yourself at home.

38:20.486 --> 38:22.142
Thanks.

38:22.177 --> 38:26.557
So you can be in there all during lunch
when you eat your two sandwiches.

38:26.569 --> 38:27.603
Two sandwiches?

38:27.638 --> 38:28.449
Oh. Yes.

38:28.484 --> 38:30.747
You'll be buying two sandwiches off the cart.

38:30.747 --> 38:32.111
The ones that aren't moving.

38:32.111 --> 38:34.983
Usually it's liverwurst and tongue.

38:35.628 --> 38:36.815
Bye.

38:38.956 --> 38:41.678
Joke's on you! I like tongue!

38:46.964 --> 38:49.467
Will the defendant please rise?

38:53.095 --> 38:55.618
Has the jury reached unanimous verdict?

38:55.653 --> 38:56.994
We have, Your Honor.

38:57.029 --> 38:58.224
What say you?

38:58.225 --> 39:01.062
In the matter of the Commonwealth versus
Irma Levine,

39:01.062 --> 39:04.023
on the count of open and gross lewdness
and lascivious behavior,

39:04.023 --> 39:05.558
we find the defendant,

39:06.026 --> 39:07.555
not guilty.

39:07.590 --> 39:09.000
Ladies and gentlemen of the jury

39:09.000 --> 39:10.541
we thank you for your services.

39:10.541 --> 39:11.809
Courts adjourned.

39:14.408 --> 39:16.243
Congratulations.

39:16.493 --> 39:17.597
I think you're closing made all

39:17.597 --> 39:19.404
the difference. Thank you very much.

39:19.404 --> 39:21.176
You're welcome. And about your protest.

39:21.176 --> 39:23.047
Next time try pasties.

39:27.713 --> 39:29.673
Well? Alan?

39:30.049 --> 39:31.849
Thank you.

39:31.884 --> 39:35.904
