to me in public courtroom?

39:36.215 --> 39:38.515
Walk me out?

39:42.936 --> 39:46.148
Excuse me? This elevator's taken.

39:58.910 --> 40:00.704
Oh my.

40:03.790 --> 40:06.584
Suddenly I'm feeling all the hope

40:06.619 --> 40:09.379
and the anticipation and the ever so

40:09.463 --> 40:12.340
slight trepidation of election day.

