Ugh! What is this?

41:09.814 --> 41:11.482
Diet Scotch. It's Bev's idea.

41:11.482 --> 41:14.527
She wants me to slim down for the wedding.

41:20.908 --> 41:23.578
I've been wondering, Denny. Are we drifting?

41:23.613 --> 41:24.155
Drifting?

41:24.190 --> 41:24.819
Apart.

41:24.854 --> 41:25.456
Apart?

41:25.491 --> 41:26.177
Yes.

41:26.212 --> 41:27.731
No!

41:27.766 --> 41:29.250
Good.

41:37.550 --> 41:39.670
I'm gonna miss you, Denny once you're married.

41:39.670 --> 41:41.602
I'm not going anywhere.

41:41.637 --> 41:44.932
